reviews.review_text: Great Recording!! THIS RECORDING IS AWESOME, the show rocks. A must have for your collection. Thanks!!

Nassau This is Killer ! I was there and this and the next night were perfect .Branford sounded like he'd been with the band since 1965 ! He immediately understood what the Dead were all about.They had other Sax players sit in ,but this 
tops 'em all...Also the band was smokin' even before he came out ...Jack Straw is Smokin'
Best sounding source This beats out the other aud copies of this famous show.  Keith L's is probably second.
